{"title":"少女颂——抄自“我的马头琴歌集”","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":8,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"少女颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——抄自“我的马头琴歌集”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原上朝霞升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像金子一样闪耀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里有一位少女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比云雀起得还早。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她披着红的头巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她提着绿的水壶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向一道泉水奔跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们都叫她：“云雀”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“云雀”她来到水边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同是一支火焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的脸映在水上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水花也跟着飞溅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当她喝下一口水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是多么幸福。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听那欢乐的笑声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声唤醒了草原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，少女，我看见你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矫健地攀上钻塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在塔顶上把手一招，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向白云鄂博问好。（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的手是一把钥匙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把草原的门打开了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福在呼唤着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也把幸福找到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，少女，我看见你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在一座高峰上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上是朵朵白云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下是垒垒石矿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们祖国的矿石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是世界上的珍宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你呀，人间的云雀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在它的头顶上飞着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一座高峰之上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的彩衫在飘扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一道长虹照着草原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着你们住的篷帐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壶里的泉水发响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手上的矿石闪亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你呀，祖国的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把这里当做第二家乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把泉水当做奶汁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把野花插在头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把水壶，一块岩芯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着你思索幻想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着你攀登钻塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶起那铁的钻杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在草原高高的塔顶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，少女，你是太阳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1956年7月，寄自草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕白云鄂博是内蒙草原上的一座大矿山，它的铁矿，据许多专家研究以后，判断为是世界上最好的铁矿之一。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}